  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Make 100–150 quality calls per session</li><li>Set appointments and get attractive incentives for closures.</li><li>Script and training provided.</li><li>Share your availability (e.g. 3 / 6 months or 1 year)</li></ul><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Good phone communication skills</li><li>Self-motivated and target-driven</li><li>Able to speak fluent English and Mandarin</li><li>SG / PR may apply, university students are welcome</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Location:</strong> Near Maxwell MRT<br /><strong>Working Hours: </strong>Monday - Friday (Min 4 hours, 4 days weekly)<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> $12-15 per hour + Incentives <br /><br />Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. </p><ul></ul>",
